trans-unit.source: Identifies the level type for a switch.
This attribute is intended to be applied to all classes that inherit from the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch> class.
trans-unit.target: Dette attributtet skal gjelde for alle klasser som arver fra <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch>klasse.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch>

trans-unit.source: The purpose of the attribute is to identify the type that specifies the switch criteria of the switch.
trans-unit.target: Formålet med attributtet er å identifisere typen som angir switch kriteriene bryteren.

trans-unit.source: Each switch determines whether a trace is to be written, based on whether an event type matches or exceeds the value of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SwitchLevelAttribute.SwitchLevelType%2A> property for the switch.
trans-unit.target: Hver bryter bestemmer om en sporing skrives, basert på om en hendelsestype samsvarer med eller større enn verdien for den <xref:System.Diagnostics.SwitchLevelAttribute.SwitchLevelType%2A>egenskapen bryteren.</xref:System.Diagnostics.SwitchLevelAttribute.SwitchLevelType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The type used for the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SwitchLevelAttribute.SwitchLevelType%2A> property varies for different switches.
trans-unit.target: Typen som brukes til den <xref:System.Diagnostics.SwitchLevelAttribute.SwitchLevelType%2A>egenskapen varierer for ulike bytter.</xref:System.Diagnostics.SwitchLevelAttribute.SwitchLevelType%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, the switch level type for the <xref:System.Diagnostics.BooleanSwitch> class is <xref:System.Boolean>, and the switch level type for the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSwitch> class is <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceLevel>.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel switch nivå typen for den <xref:System.Diagnostics.BooleanSwitch>klasse <xref:System.Boolean>, og hvilken switch nivå for <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSwitch>klassen er <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceLevel>.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceLevel> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSwitch> </xref:System.Boolean> </xref:System.Diagnostics.BooleanSwitch>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SwitchLevelAttribute"></xref> class, specifying the type that determines whether a trace should be written.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SwitchLevelAttribute"> </xref> klassen å angi typen som bestemmer om en sporing må skrives.

trans-unit.source: The `switchLevelType` parameter identifies the type that is used by the switch to determine if a trace should be written; for example, the type of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSwitch.Level%2A> property of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSwitch> class is <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceLevel>.
trans-unit.target: Den `switchLevelType` parameteren identifiserer typen som brukes av bryteren til å fastsette om må en sporing skrives; for eksempel type <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSwitch.Level%2A>-egenskapen for <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSwitch>klassen er <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceLevel>.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceLevel> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSwitch> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSwitch.Level%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> that determines whether a trace should be written.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>som bestemmer om en sporing må skrives.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the type that determines whether a trace should be written.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir typen som bestemmer om en sporing må skrives.

trans-unit.source: The level property of a switch is not necessarily named `Level`; for example, the level property of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.BooleanSwitch> class is <xref:System.Diagnostics.BooleanSwitch.Enabled%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen nivå for en bryter ikke nødvendigvis navn `Level`, for eksempel egenskapen nivå for <xref:System.Diagnostics.BooleanSwitch>klassen er <xref:System.Diagnostics.BooleanSwitch.Enabled%2A>.</xref:System.Diagnostics.BooleanSwitch.Enabled%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.BooleanSwitch>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> that determines whether a trace should be written.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>som bestemmer om en sporing må skrives.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.target: Set-operasjon mislyktes fordi verdien <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.
